  "page": "Lady Staunton",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><table class=\"infobox\" style=\"min-width:22em;max-width:32em;border-collapse:separate;border-spacing:3px\"><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;font-size:125%;font-weight:bold;font-weight:bold; background: none; line-height: 1.1em;\"><table style=\"width:100%\"><tbody><tr><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:top;text-align:left;width:50px\"><img alt=\"No image.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/1/1d/No_image.svg/50px-No_image.svg.png\" width=\"50\" height=\"50\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/1/1d/No_image.svg/75px-No_image.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/1/1d/No_image.svg/100px-No_image.svg.png 2x\" /></td><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:middle;text-align:center;padding:0px 7px 5px 7px\">Lady Staunton</td><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:top;text-align:right;width:50px\"><a href=\"/index.php/House_Staunton\" title=\"House Staunton\"><img alt=\"House Staunton.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/9/9e/House_Staunton.svg/50px-House_Staunton.svg.png\" width=\"50\" height=\"55\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/9/9e/House_Staunton.svg/75px-House_Staunton.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/9/9e/House_Staunton.svg/100px-House_Staunton.svg.png 2x\" /></a></td></tr></tbody></table></th></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center\"></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Titles</th><td>\n<div class=\"plainlist\"><ul><li>Lady of <a href=\"/index.php/Rook%27s_Rest\" title=\"Rook&#39;s Rest\">Rook's Rest</a></li><li>Dowager Lady of Rook's Rest</li></ul></div></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Allegiances</th><td>\n<div class=\"plainlist\"><ul><li><a href=\"/index.php/House_Staunton\" title=\"House Staunton\">House Staunton</a></li><li><a href=\"/index.php/Blacks\" title=\"Blacks\">Blacks</a></li></ul></div></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Culture</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Crownlands\" title=\"Crownlands\">Crownlands</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Spouse</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Lord_Staunton\" title=\"Lord Staunton\">Lord Staunton</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Book</th><td>\n<i><a href=\"/index.php/Fire_%26_Blood\" title=\"Fire &amp; Blood\">Fire &amp; Blood</a></i> (mentioned)</td></tr></tbody></table>\n<p><b>Lady Staunton</b> was the wife of <a href=\"/index.php/Lord_Staunton\" title=\"Lord Staunton\">Lord Staunton</a>, the ruling Lord of <a href=\"/index.php/Rook%27s_Rest\" title=\"Rook&#39;s Rest\">Rook's Rest</a> and head of <a href=\"/index.php/House_Staunton\" title=\"House Staunton\">House Staunton</a> during the <a href=\"/index.php/Dance_of_the_Dragons\" title=\"Dance of the Dragons\">Dance of the Dragons</a>. Her given name and birth house are unknown.\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"History\">History</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Lady_Staunton&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: History\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>After the execution of her <a href=\"/index.php/Lord_Staunton\" title=\"Lord Staunton\">husband</a> at the <a href=\"/index.php/Battle_of_Rook%27s_Rest\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Battle of Rook&#39;s Rest\">Battle of Rook's Rest</a>, Lady Staunton took charge of House Staunton. During the <a href=\"/index.php/Hour_of_the_Wolf\" title=\"Hour of the Wolf\">Hour of the Wolf</a>, when Lord <a href=\"/index.php/Cregan_Stark\" title=\"Cregan Stark\">Cregan Stark</a> and his <a href=\"/index.php/Northmen\" title=\"Northmen\">northmen</a> took control of <a href=\"/index.php/King%27s_Landing\" title=\"King&#39;s Landing\">King's Landing</a> and secured the young king <a href=\"/index.php/Aegon_III_Targaryen\" title=\"Aegon III Targaryen\">Aegon III Targaryen</a>, she rode from <a href=\"/index.php/Duskendale\" title=\"Duskendale\">Duskendale</a> to <a href=\"/index.php/King%27s_Landing\" title=\"King&#39;s Landing\">King's Landing</a> with the armies of Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Corwyn_Corbray\" title=\"Corwyn Corbray\">Corwyn Corbray</a> and Lord <a href=\"/index.php/Clement_Celtigar\" title=\"Clement Celtigar\">Clement Celtigar</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfabaftermath_-_the_hour_of_the_wolf.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfabaftermath_-_the_hour_of_the_wolf.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Lady_Staunton&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rfabaftermath_-_the_hour_of_the_wolf.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rfabaftermath_-_the_hour_of_the_wolf.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/Fire_%26_Blood\" title=\"Fire &amp; Blood\">Fire &amp; Blood</a></i>, Aftermath - The Hour of the Wolf.</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div></div>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260405005705\nCache expiry: 1209600\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.059 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.240 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 445/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 10410/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 5643/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 517/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 7/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\nUnstrip recursion depth: 0/20\nUnstrip post‐expand size: 645/5000000 bytes\nLua time usage: 0.170/7.000 seconds\nLua virtual size: 6.43 MB/50 MB\nLua estimated memory usage: 0 bytes\n-->\n<!--\nTra